{"tid":812034,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實(a^3+b^3)^(1/3)係幾何上有咩意義","createTime":"2018-09-09T10:30:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T03:49:52.000Z","uid":137768,"like":8,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d96ad3a607e864cc9987cca78d76c077f60b4b98","tid":812034,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T10:30:29.000Z","msg":"例如如果a路係3米 b路係4米<br />\n(a^1+b^1)^(1/1) = 3 + 4 = 7米<br />\n姐係A路同B路成一直線時行嘅距離<br />\n<br />\n(a^2+b^2)^(1/2) = (9 + 16)^0.5 = 5米<br />\n亦係a路同b路成直角時 打斜行去嘅距離<br />\n<br />\n咁(a^3+b^3)^(1/3) = 4.498...米 係表達緊啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋 去到4,5,6次方 甚至無限 又有無咩特別意思呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be29f8ac3b1a6061c0f3b6407cbc0536e60e2881","tid":812034,"uid":192491,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T10:45:51.000Z","msg":"一種距離黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e5c50fa187359d563e3e5a236fd70a40c8740e6","tid":812034,"uid":87506,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T10:52:16.000Z","msg":"你有個idea不如自己花時間去研究啦<br />\n你掉個問題出來 又無人知點解"},{"pid":"eb771a205b65e84a30b51385fe53ed557632aa30","tid":812034,"uid":196484,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T10:53:38.000Z","msg":"照你用Euclidean distance 推<br />\na 一維<br />\n(a^2+b^2)^1/2 二維<br />\n(a^2+b^2+c^2)^1/2 三維<br />\n(a^2+b^2+b^2+d^2)^1/2 四維<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。如此類推到n 維Euclidean distance<br />\n<br />\n一係就係<br />\n同樣維度用唔同norm既 distance<br />\nGoogle minkowski distance"},{"pid":"da10f07262f027e0a4892c5503d53f2e2d6dc4e5","tid":812034,"uid":89956,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T10:57:02.000Z","msg":"如果x^2 = a^3, y^2 = b^3, z^2 = c^3<br />\nx^2+y^2 = z^2<br />\n咁(a^3+b^3) = (x^2+y^2) = z^2 = c^3<br />\n(a^3+b^3)^(1/3) = c<br />\n<br />\n所以應該係某種transformation掛..."},{"pid":"c49c475a5cc36dba9cc78dc7adaa4bc